public class GenericSortedLinkedList<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object

Class GenericSortedLinkedList extends comparable so that the objects that are given can be sorted; Contains methods for defining the list, inserting, and two to string methods; Much of this was taken from "Object-Oriented Data Structures using Java" by Dale, Joyce, and Weems

Version:
1.0 - CSCI-102 Project 2 - 3/30/14
Author:
Dale, Joyce, and Weems (text), Devin Visslailli (editor)
